  "time_ut": 1657434304,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0da2\u0db1\u0db4\u0dad\u0dd2 \u0db8\u0dd0\u0daf\u0dd4\u0dbb\u0dda \u0dad\u0dd2\u0db6\u0dd6 \u0db8\u0dd4\u0daf\u0dbd\u0dca \u0dad\u0ddc\u0d9c\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dca \u0d85\u0dbb\u0d9c\u0dbd\u0d9a\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0ddd \u0db4\u0ddc\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0dc3\u0dd2\u0dba \u0db6\u0dcf\u0dbb \u0daf\u0dd9\u0dad\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The activists hand over a stack of money that was in the presidential palace to the police",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "According to the police, an amount of one crore seventy eight lakh fifty thousand rupees which was in the President's House at the time of the struggle was handed over by the university students.",
        "The police also mention that the money, which was in a cupboard in the President's House, was given by the university students to a police special task force officer, and later it was handed over to the station commander of Fort Police.",
        "When the activists entered the President's House, the students of the university took the relevant money into their custody and after counting the money, recorded the video and handed over the relevant money to the police.",
        "The Fort Police also said that they are going to report the facts to the Colombo Fort Magistrate's Court regarding this amount."
      ],
